    "That is, when the angle is zero between vectors, cos (0) = 1, and their similarity becomes only the product of their magnitudes.",
    "Conversely, when the angle is 90 degrees between vectors, cos (90) = 0, and their similarity is zero, regardless of their individual magnitudes.",
